Task¶

Use your own document image.

pts_org = ([[50, 2800], # abaix esquerra
                   #[1700, 3500], # abaix dreta
                   [1200,700], # adalt esquerra
                   [2650,1500]]) # adalt dreta
 
pts_dest = np.float32([[0,altura], 
                       #[3000,4000], 
                       [0,0], 
                       [anchura,0]])

img_aux = im_photo.copy()
for p1 in pts_org:
    cv2.circle(img_aux, p1, radius = 50, color = (255,0,0), thickness=-1)

fig, (ax1) = plt.subplots(1)

In [25]:
pts_org = np.float32(pts_org)

M = cv2.getAffineTransform(pts_org, pts_dest)
dst = cv2.warpAffine(im_photo, M, (anchura, altura))
 
plt.subplot(121)
plt.imshow(im_photo)
plt.title('Input')

plt.subplot(122)
plt.imshow(dst)
plt.title('Output')
 
plt.show()
